==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Purposer
<hw>Pur"pos*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
brings forward or proposes anything; a proposer.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who forms a purpose; one who intends.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Purposive</ent>⟦br⟧
